window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Astrid continues her battle with the Corruption and betrayal that is engulfing Rebirth.</b></p> <p>Monsters, the Order, and invaders from the vast space above threaten the destruction of the world. Left without options, Astrid's only remaining method is to destroy everything in her path if she wants her family to make it to the end.</p> <p>Astrid will power-up, gain mighty upgrades to her current abilities, and put a stop to the evil that plagues Ruiteraâ€”or die trying.</p> <p>The end is nigh, but for Astrid, it is merely just the beginning of her otherworldly supremacy.</p> <p><b>Book three of an action-packed and often hilarious LitRPG apocalypse series about a young survivor with a craving for adventure and fighting. Perfect for fans of </b><b><i>Azarinth Healer</i></b><b> and </b><b><i>Eight</i></b><b>.</b></p>"; 
